 Thursday, November 13, 2008 
 
  
 
 It great to hear from everyone! 
 
  
 
 Hey all! I just wanted to pop in and give you an update.  First of all, Mrs. R is pregnant and due February 8th. We're very excited and cannot wait to meet our little girl!  Secondly, its great to hear from everyone. I receive an email each time one of you posts on the blog, so feel free to keep in touch. If you would like to contact me my e-mail is  ariccardo@schools.nyc.gov   Miss you all and have a nice holiday season!  Mr. R 
  
 
 
 

