 Saturday, July 5, 2008 
 
  
 
 Enjoy Your Summer Vacation! 
 
  
 
 Hello all! I hope everyone is enjoying the summer so far. This is a great time to see some of the amazing things happening all around the New York area. From the beaches, to the parks, and even your own backyard there are multiple opportunities to see much of the natural world. Get out there and enjoy it. If you see anything really cool, post it on the blog. Let others share in your discovery. Enjoy, get outside, and have a great summer! 
  
 
 
 

